“The clearest way into the Universe is through a forest wilderness.” ― John Muir
Tibumana Waterfall – Located in central Bali, very near from Ubud, is where you will witness this pulchritudinous waterfall.
In the Bangli regency, Tibumana Waterfall is one of the most beautiful hidden waterfalls to see in Bali. The mountain,lakes, rice terrace views and lush valleys - all scattered throughout its rich landscape.

The cliffs in this spot are overgrown with vegetation, which enhances this magnificent waterfall and natural pool.
